12namespace v8::internal::compiler::turboshaft {
13
14struct RuntimeCallDescriptor {
15 private:
16 template <typename Derived>
17 struct Descriptor {
18 static const TSCallDescriptor* Create(Zone* zone) {
19 auto descriptor = Linkage::GetRuntimeCallDescriptor(
20 zone, Derived::kFunction,
21 std::tuple_size_v<typename Derived::arguments_t>,
22 Derived::kProperties,
23 Derived::kNeedsFrameState ? CallDescriptor::kNeedsFrameState
24 : CallDescriptor::kNoFlags);
25#ifdef DEBUG
26 Derived::Verify(descriptor);
27#endif // DEBUG
28 CanThrow can_throw = (Derived::kProperties & Operator::kNoThrow)
29 ? CanThrow::kNo
30 : CanThrow::kYes;
31 return TSCallDescriptor::Create(descriptor, can_throw, zone);
32 }
33
34#ifdef DEBUG
35 static void Verify(const CallDescriptor* desc) {
36 using result_t = typename Derived::result_t;
37 using arguments_t = typename Derived::arguments_t;
38 if constexpr (std::is_same_v<result_t, void>) {
39 DCHECK_EQ(desc->ReturnCount(), 0);
40 } else {
41 DCHECK_EQ(desc->ReturnCount(), 1);
42 DCHECK(result_t::allows_representation(
43 RegisterRepresentation::FromMachineRepresentation(
44 desc->GetReturnType(0).representation())));
45 }
46 DCHECK_EQ(desc->NeedsFrameState(), Derived::kNeedsFrameState);
47 DCHECK_EQ(desc->properties(), Derived::kProperties);
48 constexpr int additional_stub_arguments =
49 3; // function id, argument count, context (or NoContextConstant)
50 DCHECK_EQ(desc->ParameterCount(),
51 std::tuple_size_v<arguments_t> + additional_stub_arguments);
52 DCHECK(VerifyArguments<arguments_t>(desc));
53 }
54
55 template <typename Arguments>
56 static bool VerifyArguments(const CallDescriptor* desc) {
57 return VerifyArgumentsImpl<Arguments>(
58 desc, std::make_index_sequence<std::tuple_size_v<Arguments>>());
59 }
60
61 private:
62 template <typename Arguments, size_t... Indices>
63 static bool VerifyArgumentsImpl(const CallDescriptor* desc,
64 std::index_sequence<Indices...>) {
65 return (std::tuple_element_t<Indices, Arguments>::allows_representation(
66 RegisterRepresentation::FromMachineRepresentation(
67 desc->GetParameterType(Indices).representation())) &&
68 ...);
69 }
70#endif // DEBUG
71 };
72
73 public:
74 struct Abort : public Descriptor<Abort> {
75 static constexpr auto kFunction = Runtime::kAbort;
76 using arguments_t = std::tuple<V<Smi>>;
77 using result_t = V<Object>;
78
79 static constexpr bool kNeedsFrameState = false;
80 static constexpr Operator::Properties kProperties =
81 Operator::kNoDeopt | Operator::kNoThrow;
82 };
83

88

90 static constexpr Operator::Properties kProperties =
91 Operator::kNoDeopt | Operator::kNoThrow;
92 };

102 };

175 : public Descriptor<ThrowAccessedUninitializedVariable> {
176 static constexpr auto kFunction =
177 Runtime::kThrowAccessedUninitializedVariable;
178 using arguments_t = std::tuple<V<Object>>;
179 // Doesn't actually return something, but the actual runtime call descriptor
180 // (returned by Linkage::GetRuntimeCallDescriptor) returns 1 instead of 0.
181 using result_t = V<Object>;
182
183 static constexpr bool kNeedsFrameState = true;
184 static constexpr Operator::Properties kProperties = Operator::kNoProperties;
185 };
186};
